column5: Hey gang,  First off, I'd like to extend a big warm thanks to everyone here at OFC.  Good things are on the go and it has a lot to do with the good folks in this community.  Second, HAPPY NEW YEAR!!  It's been a fantastic 2010.  Lots of epic trips, new friends and lessons learned afield.  All these threads with pics and music have offered quite the inspiration, so here's a montage of my own with some of the years best, plus a few randoms for a little comic relief.  So sit back, pop a brew and turn the speakers up!!  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eOLQETaJe6E  cheers!! HD
nice fish but i had to turn the music off cause it was giving me a headache and now i think i have a brain tumor
HAHAAH!!  Sorry bout that..  This is happy music to some, finger nails accross a chalk board to others...
Love it!  Brings back some great memories buddy. It was a great year.
SAY WHAT !!! . CAN YA SPEAK UP A WEE BIT.  dude !!! excellent vid, ma man. ya had an excellent season HD. snappy new year to ya too.  Paul
Great vid...lots of fishy faces. I liked the song...who's it by?
Them Crooked Vultures - Reptiles.
And a groovy New Year to you too bud!
oh ya...i should have known Josh Holmes was involved.
Lots of nice fish and good times are shown there.  Great meeting you when on the lakefront walking with my daughter. She sensed you were a good guy
Really?!  I didn't look like a total sketch ball hunched over like that?!  All the best to you and yours this year Erik.
Good times meng! Lots of variety there for sure. Hope this year keeps 'em on yer hook!
Darn tooting budday!  Looking forward to icing a few in Haliburton with ya..

Awesome video Fidel Lots of beauties in this footage That's some funky tunes.... had to replay it a couples of times   but it grows on ya Thanks for sharing your time along the shoreline with us!!! Jacques
Ma man,  Jacques!
Lots of good fish there. Have a great 2011 season buddy.
Awesome video Fidel, really enjoyed that  Joey
Well done man.  I fished somewhere in the neighbourhood of 4 or 5 times this year.  Cheers.  I hate you :-)

Quite enjoyed that man.  You sure got out with a tonne of different folks in different places. All adds up to experience.  2011 must be something you're looking forward to.  I'll be keeping an eye out for HD reports as always.... good luck.
I must be blind, how'd I miss this?  Nice vid buddy, here's to an even better 2011.
